title: Fantastic Four Annual (001 - 027,32,33 + Extras) (1963 - 2012)
description:
Fantastic Four Annual (001 - 027,32,33 + Extras) (1963 - 2012)


The series ran from 1963-1994 for twenty-seven issues. From 1998-2001 had unique indicia titles;

Fantastic Four / Fantastic 4 '98
Uncanny X-Men / Fantastic Four '98 (The Uncanny X-Men Annual)
Fantastic Four 1999
Fantastic Four 2000
Fantastic Four 2001
The series resumed in 2010 with issue #32.
